*kdebase-startkde-3.5.6-r1 (28 Jan 2007)

  28 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +kdebase-startkde-3.5.6-r1.ebuild:
  Fix KDE environment variables not to export XDG_CONFIG_DIRS to non-KDE
  serssions. Thanks to Christoph Brill for reporting and Pacho Ramos for
  finding the problem again. See bug #164034.

  19 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-startkde-3.5.6.ebuild:
  Depend on kdelibs 3.5.6, and then drop the xdg.sh env file, as we already
  set that in env.d.

